    "text": "Tools like Visual Studio, sure, they could utilize the effort of 50 people. But that's not a language, it's a tool that has to integrate with a _ton_ of other tools. And yes, anything that unifies AWS needs to integrate with all the pieces of AWS... but that's just wrapping up a bunch of APIs, not an effort-intensive large scale task.",
